by-step study of each of the various human faculties of cognition, a study that is much like the process of putting together the pieces of a puzzle.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aKnowledge, Theory ofvEarly works to 1800. 0aLogic, Ancient. 0aNoos (The Greek word). 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010z978311127416408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010z978311127724040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978276371448640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763714486423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763714486/original  a978-3-11-127416-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010b2010  a978-3-11-127724-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010b2010  aGBV-deGruyter-alles